00:21:32.640 --> 00:21:35.560
BENAR!  Tapi kita harus
segera menangani Sandy.

00:21:36.240 --> 00:21:39.120
Maksudku, dia tidak bisa
memerasmu seperti ini.

00:21:40.440 --> 00:21:41.760
Drashti!

00:21:50.160 --> 00:21:51.680
Apa apaan!

00:21:55.080 --> 00:21:56.240
Apa semua ini?

